<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome to Aveta AI</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        color: #111827;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 24px;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background-color: #7f56d9;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 40px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Welcome to Aveta, <%= name %>!</h2>
      <p>
        We're excited to have you on board. Aveta AI is here to help you, create
        your own desire characters and chat with them.
      </p>
      <p>You can log in to your account anytime using the button below:</p>
      <a href="<%= homeUrl %>" class="btn">Go to Aveta</a>

      <p style="margin-top: 24px">
        If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email — we're
        always happy to help.
      </p>
      <p>With appreciation,<br />— The Aveta Team</p>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          This email was sent to <%= email %>. If this wasn't you, please ignore
          it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
